text: Axel Wöstmann (born 12 April 1961) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Osnabrück
